name: Space Frog X
description: Space Frog X is a meme-based cryptocurrency that combines humor and functionality to create a unique ecosystem for its users. The project offers various utilities, including a decentralized swap platform, staking features for passive income, AI integration, and a blockchain-based game currently in development. Inspired by a viral frog meme and Elon Musk's SpaceX, Space Frog X seeks to engage its community while providing practical blockchain applications.
